---
description: Agent workflow and planning rules
alwaysApply: true
---

- Start each major task by identifying the current milestone from PLAN.md.
- Before editing, state the files you expect to change.
- Work in small, reviewable batches.
- Do not silently refactor unrelated areas.
- After each batch, summarize: completed work, blockers, next step.
- If the requested scope exceeds the current milestone, propose a phased approach instead of doing everything at once.
